# **1. Getting Started**

## **1.1 Installing and loading the packages**



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
pacman::p_load(tidyverse)
```
:::



## **1.2 Data import**



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
exam_data <- read_csv("data/Exam_data.csv")
```
:::



# **2. Plotting Visualization**

## 2.1 Boxplot 



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(data=exam_data, 
       aes(x = ENGLISH,       
           y= CLASS)) +    
  geom_boxplot()            
```
